Third Coast FRC Library

Stryke Force 2767 Third Coast swerve drive, talon configuration and telemetry API for FRC robots.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.swerve
Third Coast swerve drive API.
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.talon
Support for configuring instances of CANTalon with a TOML configuration file.
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry
Provides a data streaming service for robot sensors, actuators or subsystems.
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry.grapher
Support for Third Coast Telemetry Grapher client.
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry.item
Robot sensors, actuators or subsystems that are telemetry-enabled.
org.strykeforce.thirdcoast.telemetry.util
Contains waveform generators for the Telemetry simulator developement tool and other utility classes.

Stryke Force 2767 Third Coast swerve drive, talon configuration and telemetry API for FRC robots.

More documentation is available at Stryke Force Engineering .
